manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Previous page Next page 1 100% SUGAR-FREE 2 ALLERGEN FREE 3 NO JUNK OR FILLERS 4 100% VEGAN

How many calories are in Nutramin Kids Gummies? Is there any sugar? There are just 5 calories in each gummy, with .5 carbs, 0 fat, and 0 sugar. Most gummies are full of sugar, syrups and artificial sweeteners, making them unhealthy. That's why Nutramin is naturally sweetened with stevia leaf. Are all the ingredients in Nutramin vegan-sourced? Made with real apple pectin, Nutramin kids contains no gelatine or other animal-sourced ingredients. Nutramin's naturally-sourced nutrients are extracted from real plants & fruits - never cheaper synthetics - to help boost your immune function. Is Nutramin safe for kids with food allergies? Absolutely! Nutramin contains NO Eggs, Milk, Mustard, Peanuts, Crustaceans and Molluscs, Fish, Sesame Seeds, Soy, Sulphites, Tree Nuts, Wheat or Triticale. Proudly Made in the USA in FDA approved peanut-free and tree-nut free factory. Who is Nutramin Kids for? OUR ALLERGY-SAFE VEGAN GELATIN-FREE & KETO GUMMY Multivites for Toddlers, Children & Teens are made with pure Apple Pectin in natural Strawberry, Cherry & Orange flavours, and do NOT contain any animal-sourced or synthetics. How long will a bottle last? Each bottle has 90 gummies, so there is a 45 day supply for one child.

DISCOVER OUR INGREDIENTS VITAMIN A From 100% natural fat-soluble beta-carotene, not cheaper synthetics. VITAMIN C Extracted from real fruit, never synthetic ascorbic acid found in other multivitamin brands. VITAMIN D3 Plant-based vitamin D3 from lichen, instead of cheaper animal-sourced sources. VITAMIN E Extracted from natural plant-sources for maximum effectiveness. VITAMIN B6 Naturally-sourced from nutritional yeast. FOLIC ACID We use vegan-sourced folate, which is almost 100% bioavailable, unlike synthentic types. VITAMIN B12 Only naturally-sourced Methylcobalamin, NOT the cheaper & less effective Cyanocobalamin. BIOTIN Our plant-based, vegan biotin is not derived from animal sources like most other brands. PANTOTHENIC ACID We never use chemically-synthesized alternatives or animal-sourced ingredients. ZINC Plant-based zinc from beans, chickpeas and lentils. CHOLINE Naturally sources from from beans, chickpeas, lentils, and greens. IODINE Vegan sourced iodine, not chemically-synthesized alternatives or animal-sourced. INOSITOL Naturally sourced inositol from brewers yeast. OTHER INGREDIENTS: Water, apple pectin, citric acid, sodium citrate, natural flavor, refined coconut oil (hypoallergenic), carnauba wax, stevia leaf extract.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Helps with my sons mood
reviews.reviewText: I recently tried the Kids Mood Gummies for my 7-year-old, and I must say, I'm thoroughly impressed! As a parent, finding a product that combines fun, flavor, and wellness is like striking gold, and these gummies hit the mark.First off, the taste is a big win. My child is quite picky, but these gummies have been a game-changer. She looks forward to her 'special treat' every day without any fuss, which is a relief.What really sets these gummies apart is their effectiveness. I've noticed a visible uplift in her mood and overall demeanor. It's like these gummies add a little extra sunshine to her day, making her more resilient and cheerful.The natural ingredients list gives me peace of mind, knowing I'm not compromising on health for convenience. It's comforting to have a product that supports her emotional well-being without any artificial nasties.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Moves those bowels!!!
reviews.reviewText: We die hard love these vitamins. We’ve tried everything straight through to GI appointments and medication to help my daughter have regular bowel movements her entire life but nothing worked consistently or in healthy ways. Finally we started her on these! The first time we gave her two (she’s a tiny four year old) her poop was green, so we knew maybe it needed a minute to process in her system so we pulled back to one a day. Soon she was pooping every day or other day. Even with one a day if she starts going on day three or almost day four without poop, we just start giving her two of these vitamins a day and within 24 hours she’s back on track! Seriously I can’t live without these now, it saved us from having to always give her Doctor prescribed Miralax causing bathroom accidents and being so stopped up we have to go to urgent care- so far after not even finishing one bottle I haven’t felt a single nerve about her bowels. So so grateful for these vitamins. They also taste amazing she’s had zero complaints. We emptied them into this beautiful unicorn container I ordered separately (like a metal screw on thermos type) and call them “unicorn dots” and whether she needs one or two that day she is happy to down them after breakfast! Thank you for designing these!
